description: If you enjoy healthy meals made from produce that is farm-to-table, 100% organic, and locally sourced, then there is much reason to rejoice! Rejuice is serving L.A. with top-choice vegan cuisine, as well as cold-pressed juices and smoothies. Take a trip over to sip on their refreshing selection of made-to-order juices made with the freshest fruits and vegetables. With great juice, comes their great sandwiches, wraps, and salads. You’ll love The Portobello Muffaletta - complete with Portabello, pickled Olive & Vegetable Tapenade, and Roasted Red Peppers. The 5-Spiced Tofu Wrap and Kale Salad are other favorites, just to name a few. No matter what you choose, you’ll give your day a little spruce when you head on down to visit Rejuice.
name: Rejuice
